Sorcery Studios. The "Core (PHB)" races, "DMG" races, and "Monster Manual"
races are from (respectively) the "Player's Handbook", "Dungeon Master's
Guide", and the "Monster Manual", all Copyright 2000 by Wizards of the Coast.
The character classes, skills, feats, spells, and level progression rules are
from the Player's Handbook and the Dungeon Master's Guide.  The above races,
classes, skills, feats, and rules also exist in the System Reference Document
(http://www.opengamingfoundation.org/srd.html) of the Open Gaming License.
The "Creature Collection" races are from the "Creature Collection" by Sword
and Sorcery Studios.

All other aspects of this program, including the algorithms for generating a
random non-player character, are released in the PUBLIC DOMAIN.

